What our users say?

A very good project. Grass creates a way to reward people for their unused internet bandwidth while maintaining personal data security at the same time. Hoping for more great updates to come.

Read More

Elijah Parker

The website and desktop app are functioning well and are extremely user-friendly. All that's left is the release of the mobile app, which I am eagerly awaiting. I appreciate the seamless experience provided by all platforms and look forward to the upcoming mobile app. I'm pleased with how Grass effectively utilizes unused bandwidth, and I'm excited to contribute to the broader mission of taking back control of the internet.

Emily Wilson

It's reassuring to know that by sharing my unused internet resources, I can earn rewards through Grass. Grass provides a stake in AI, making it a standout option for those interested in taking back control of the public web. It's a win-win.

Read More

Gabriella Mancini

So far, my experiences with Grass have been great. The team is polite and helpful and seem very interested in making the project successful. The dashboard is clean and very professional-looking. Any issues that have arisen have been taken care of in a timely manner. I am an experienced user of bandwidth-sharing apps, so I base my views on the comparison of those I've been using to this project. I see a possibility of a very successful app here for all involved.

Read More

James White

Grass is a revolutionary platform that empowers people to share their internet resources and benefit from them. It's a win-win situation for everyone involved. I highly recommend Grass to anyone who wants to get exposure to AI. Grass is the future of internet access! Getting started with Grass is a breeze. The process involves three simple steps: creating an account, downloading the Grass desktop app, and keeping the extension running in the background. Once it's up and running, you can passively earn rewards without any hassle.

Read More

Eric Andreasson

5 stars plus another 5 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ I've installed the app roughly one month ago, and I have to say I'm extremely impressed! The installation process is intuitive, even for someone like me who isn't the most tech-savvy. The user interface is clear and straightforward, ensuring a hassle-free setup and operation. All it takes is setting it up once and reaping the rewards without any additional effort. Regarding security, after diving into the details and understanding how Grass works, I found out that it doesn't use any personal data. While ISPs may utilize unused bandwidth, Grass gives us a chance to benefit directly from it. It's like renting out parking space without revealing anything inside your house. I'm confident that whatever is routed through my IP remains detached from my personal activities. Most importantly, there's no drop in my internet speed. Grass intelligently taps into my unused resources without affecting my online experience. In a nutshell, Grass empowers users to get exposure to the future of AI without trading off privacy, safety, or the quality of your internet connection. If you're looking for a safe, secure, and efficient way to make the most out of your idle resources, look no further. Grass is the answer!

Read More

Johnathan Campbell

Great app! What I love about this project is its potential for success. Grass allows users to earn rewards simply by sharing unused internet bandwidth in exchange for Grass Points. By signing up, downloading the desktop app, and letting it run, you're all set! Their website is user-friendly, and they are transparent about how your points are calculated.
